  fhir:description [ fhir:v "A volume of the body used in radiotherapy planning or treatment delivery.\r\nIn ARIA, dose is specified and tracked against Reference Points. These Reference Points can represent actual points or three-dimensional volumes.\r\nARIA calls all of those 'Reference Point', even if not a point. Each Reference Point in ARIA is exposed as a Radiotherapy Volume."] ; # 
